WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:14.000
I took over a derelict building in the city, and organize it into a functional space where people could take refugee

00:14.000 --> 00:30.000
Some policemen in the area found out, but it was so well done that they got me a meeting with the town mayor

00:30.000 --> 00:37.000
He knew who I was, and gave me a permit

